column41:
The salvage code has code like this:

{noformat}
        ret = __wt_page_release(session, ref, 0);
        if (ret == 0)
                ret = __wt_evict(session, ref, true);
{noformat}

That's not safe, because eviction could have evicted the page in-between those calls.

